text: Alina Şaitan (née Bîrca, born 1 May 1991) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Women's Championship club Anenii Noi and the Moldova women's national team. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Moldova women's international footballers
